<html><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">Micro Focus OpsBridge Database Toolkit</span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">The Operations Bridge database toolkit contains tools and scripts to help with the configuration and maintenance of the databases used by Operations Bridge Manager and Suite.</span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">The toolkit has been published on Micro Focus ITOM Marketplace and may be located using this url:</span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><a href="https://marketplace.microfocus.com/itom/content/opsbridge-database-toolkit" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">https://marketplace.microfocus.com/itom/content/opsbridge-database-toolkit</a></span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">With this first release the toolkit supports the checking of performance related parameter values against those values recommended in the Micro Focus documentation for OpsBridge Manager and the containerized OpsBridge Suite.</span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">This release provides scripts for PostgreSQL and Oracle. &nbsp;You will find .sql scripts for both Oracle and PostgreSQL.&nbsp; Wrapper scripts (.sh &amp; .bat) have also been provided for linux and windows operating systems to simplify the use.</span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">The following screenshot is an example of the output on a PostgreSQL system.</span></span></span><br>
<br>
