<br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">Please know that in this release, the Check Parameters tool is used to check the OBM database's current parameter settings against the values which Micro Focus recommends for LARGE deployments. The output of the tool will only highlight parameters that DO NOT match the recommended settings.</span></span></span><br>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">For more details, please refer to the Micro Focus ITOM Marketplace page at the previously mentioned url.</span></span></span><br>
